headline: Why I've Backed the Truck and Loaded Up on These 3 High-Yield Dividend Stocks
summary: Many economists predict that President Trump's tariffs could cause inflation to increase even more.  If I were focused only on the near term, I might not touch shares of Honda Motor (NYSE: HMC) with a 10-foot pole.  Honda's planned acquisition of Nissan fell through.
